quran[86]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Yeh log kis cheez ke baarey mei puch-gajj kar rahe hain
  78,2,Kya us badi khabar ke baarey mein
  78,3,Jiske mutaaliq yeh mukhtalif che-mei-goiyan (disagreement) karne mein lagey huey hain
  78,4,Hargiz nahin an-qareeb inhein maloom ho jayega
  78,5,"Haan hargiz nahin, an-qareeb inhein maloom ho jayega"
  78,6,Kya yeh waqiya nahin hai ke humne zameen ko farsh banaya
  78,7,Aur pahadon ko mekhon(pegs) ki tarah gaad diya
  78,8,Aur tumhein (mardon aur auraton ke) jodon ki shakal mein paida kiya
  78,9,Aur tumhari neend ko baaisey sukoon banaya
  78,10,Aur raat ko purdah posh
  78,11,Aur din ko muaash ka waqt banaya
  78,12,Aur Tumharey upar saat mazboot aasman qayam kiye
  78,13,Aur ek nihayat roshan aur garm chirag paida kya
  78,14,Aur baadalon se lagatar baarish barsayi
  78,15,Taa-ke iske zariye se galla(grain) aur sabzi
  78,16,Aur ghaney baagh ugaye
  78,17,Beshak faisley ka din ek mukarrar waqt hai
  78,18,Jis roz soor mei phook maar di jayegi tum fauj dar fauj nikal aaogey
  78,19,Aur aasmaan khol diya jayega hatta ke woh darwaze hi darwaze ban kar reh jayega
  78,20,Aur pahad chalaye jayenge yahan tak ke woh saraab(mirage) ho jayenge
  78,21,Dar haqeeqat jahannum ek ghaat(ambush) hai
  78,22,Sarkashon ka thikana
  78,23,Jismein woh muddaton padey rahengey
  78,24,Uske andar kisi thandak aur peene ke qabil kisi cheez ka maza woh na chakhengey
  78,25,kuch milega to bas garam paani aur zakhmon ka dho-wan(peep)
  78,26,(Unke kartuton) ka bharpur badla
  78,27,Woh kisi hisab ki tawakku na rakhte thay
  78,28,Aur hamari aayat ko unhon ne bilkul jhutla diya tha
  78,29,Aur haal yeh tha ke humne har cheez gin gin kar likh rakkhi thi
  78,30,"Ab chakho maza, Hum tumhare liye azaab ke siwa kisi cheez mei hargiz izafa na karengey"
  78,31,Yakeenan muttakiyon(pious) ke liye kamrani ka ek Muqaam hai
  78,32,Baagh aur angur
  78,33,Aur naukhez humsin ladkiyan
  78,34,Aur jhalakte huey jaam
  78,35,Wahan koi lagv(vain) aur jhuthi baat woh na sunengey
  78,36,Jazaa aur kafi inaam tumharey Rubb ki taraf se
  78,37,Us nihayat meharban khuda ki taraf se jo zameen aur aasmaano ka aur inke darmiyan ki har cheez ka malik hai jiske samney kisi ko bolne ka yara nahin
  78,38,Jis roz rooh aur malaika saff basta khade hongey. Koi na bolega siwaye uske jisey Rehman ijazat de aur jo theek baat kahey
  78,39,"Woh din bar-haqq hai, ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf palatne ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  78,40,"Humne tum logon ko us azaab se dara diya hai jo qareeb aa laga hai. Jis roz aadmi woh sab kuch dekh lega jo uske hathon ne aagey bheja hai, aur kafir pukar uthega ke kaash mai khaaq(mitti) hota"
  79,1,Kasam hai un (Farishton) ki jo doob kar khinchte hain
  79,2,aur aahistagi se (gently) nikaal le jataey hain
  79,3,Aur (un farishton ki jo qayinaat mein) tezi se tairtey phirtay hain
  79,4,phir (hukum baja laane mein) sabqat karte hain
  79,5,phir (ehkam-ilahi ke mutabiq) maamlaat ka intizam chalate hain
  79,6,Jis roz hila marey ga zalzalay ka jhatka
  79,7,Aur uske pichey ek aur jhatka padega
  79,8,Kuch dil hongey jo us roz khauf se kaanp rahey hongey
  79,9,Nigahein unki sehmi(downcast) hui hogi
  79,10,Yeh log kehte hain “Kya waqai hum palta kar phir wapas laaye jayenge?”
  79,11,“Kya jab hum khokli boseeda (hollow and rotten) haddiyan ban chuke hongey?”
  79,12,Kehne lagey “yeh wapsi to phir badey ghatey(nuksan) ki hogi”
  79,13,Halaanke yeh bas itna kaam hai ke ek zoar ki daant padegi
  79,14,Aur yakayk yeh khule maidan mein maujood hongey
  79,15,Kya tumhein Moosa ke qissey ki khabar pahunchi hai
  79,16,Jab uske Rubb ne usey Tuwa ke muqaddas wadi(valley) mein pukara tha
  79,17,"Ke Firaun ke paas ja, woh sarkash ho gaya hai"
  79,18,"Aur ussey keh, kya tu iske liye tayyar hai ke pakeezgi ikhtiyar karey"
  79,19,Aur mai terey Rubb ki taraf teri rehnumai karoon to (uska) khauf terey andar paida ho?”
  79,20,Phir Moosa ne (Firaun ke paas ja kar) usko badi nishani dikhai
  79,21,Magar usne jhutla diya aur na mana
  79,22,Phir chaal baaziyan karne ke liye palta
  79,23,Aur logon ko jama karke usne pukaar kar kaha
  79,24,“Main tumhara sabse bada Rubb hoon”
  79,25,Aakhir-e-kaar Allah ne usey aakhirat aur duniya ke azaab mei pakad liya
  79,26,Dar haqeeqat is mein badi ibrat hai har us shaks ke liye jo darey
  79,27,Kya tum logon ki takhleeq(paidaish) zyada sakht kaam hai ya aasmaan ki? Allah ne usko banaya
  79,28,Uski chhat(ceiling) khoob unchi uthayi phir uska tawazun qayam kiya(proportioned it)
  79,29,Aur uski raat dhaanki aur uska din nikala
  79,30,Iske baad zameen ko usne bichaya
  79,31,Uske andar se uska paani aur chara nikala
  79,32,Aur pahad usmein gaadh diye
  79,33,Saaman-e-zeist(provision) ke taur par tumharay liye aur tumharey maweshion ke liye
  79,34,Phir jab woh hungama-e-azeem barpa hoga
  79,35,Jis roz Insan apna sab kiya dhara yaad karega
  79,36,Aur har dekhne wale ke samney dozak khol kar rakh di jayegi
  79,37,To jisne sarkashi(transgress) ki thi
  79,38,Aur dunya ki zindagi ko tarjeeh di thi
  79,39,dozakh hi uska thikana hogi
  79,40,Aur jisne apne Rubb ke samney khade honay ka khauf kiya tha aur nafs ko buri khwaishaat se baaz rakha tha
  79,41,Jannat uska thikana hogi
  79,42,Yeh log tumse puchte hain ke aakhir woh ghadi kab aakar thehre gi
  79,43,Tumhara kya kaam ke us ka waqt batao
  79,44,Us ka ilm to Allah par khatm hai
  79,45,Tum sirf khabardar karne waley ho har us shaks ko jo uska khauff karey
  79,46,Jis roz yeh log usey dekh lengey to inhein yun mehsoos hoga ke (yeh duniya mein ya halat-e-mout mei) bas ek din ke pichle pehar ya aglay pehar tak thehrey hai